"""Offline unit tests for the SQLAlchemy unit of work.

These exercise the async transaction adapter against in-memory async SQLite,
so the unit-of-work boundary stays covered without Docker. The fast offline
tier runs on ``sqlite+aiosqlite`` regardless of the project's runtime database.
"""
